{"tid":2358224,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣又凍，返工屙屎個廁板好凍，你會點做？","createTime":"2021-01-08T03:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T04:29:12.000Z","uid":40930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c50ab280f44875dad9e0a5373bd2c882a9267b","tid":2358224,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"帶住顆灼熱嘅心，滿腔熱忱，返工去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知坐落個廁板個下當堂縮兩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個廁板冰造？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時返工屙屎要屙得有質素，係一種態度問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要我坐上手用過嘅根本冇可能，係屈辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點先可以係寒冬中嘅公司裡屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a732f1a5f9102f7ca7d7ac0dca2b6681207e1357","tid":2358224,"uid":206522,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"岩岩先知原來有人會坐落果塊唔知幾多人踩過既廁板上面"},{"pid":"0681c9b691c2902dfdd46f46a48c13f9473b8836","tid":2358224,"uid":81312,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"正想問點解要坐落去"},{"pid":"3b4047eaaa7854d17aabdf0496962a2b4f31c7e1","tid":2358224,"uid":366457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"下，要嚟坐架咩？"},{"pid":"a3cd5c5dc8f39ae88e40aa26a35e8da6604432e8","tid":2358224,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"公廁廁板都敢坐，凍又點會難到你"},{"pid":"1d0e83a94dbc80550240cb855766e83da63103be","tid":2358224,"uid":40930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"咁多支那人同事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得支那仔先會踩上去屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as